    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#marengo2010a"/>, p. 154, n. <citedRange>25</citedRange>, fig. 5, 25</bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>113100</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <div type="textpart" n="a">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><orig>σ</orig><space extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                </ab>
                </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" n="b">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><choice><unclear>σ</unclear><unclear>μ</unclear></choice><space extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                </ab>
            </div>
        </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p>
                    <app loc="a-b">
                        <rdg resp="#marengo2010a"><orig>σ</orig> <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 
                            <choice><unclear>ν</unclear><unclear>σ</unclear><unclear>μ</unclear></choice> <note>read as a whole</note></rdg>
                    </app>
                </p>
               </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
                <p>Intraduisible.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
                <p>Not usefully translatable.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
                <p>Intraducibile.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>غير قابل للترجمة بشكل جيد</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>From the photograph, the first letter on the left is sigma; the smaller letter is either, if read without moving the vase, a mu with the left leg lost
                    or, if read after a quarter turn to the right, a sigma with the lower stroke lost. Anyway, the latter in C. Dobias-Lalou's view cannot be a nu, for the 
                    shape would refer to a date much higher than the vase and to a right-to-left script, also out of date.</p>
                <p/>
            </div></body>
    </text>
